			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Ela Rozenberg on the deportations of Jews from the Warsaw Ghetto and the transport to the Treblinka extermination
					camp. After the selection, she was assigned to sort the clothes of the murdered Jews and to bury their bodies.</p>
			</abstract>
